messages.message:
Hey team, if someone uploads an encrypted or corrupted file can we detect this? (question came from Deloitte AU for a tier 2 bank POC)

I assume solutions will flag errors but won't necessarily explain what is going wrong to a Human Reviewer. It would be useful for their to a message related to this possibility.
Actually for this one a ticket, too please :grin:. We just had the same issue where we didn't realise Excel files were password-protected and that this caused the processing issue.
